Winux OS Plymouth Boot Theme
=============================

This Plymouth theme displays the Winux OS branding during system boot.

Required Image Assets (place in this directory):
- winux-logo.png      - Main logo (recommended: 200x200 PNG with transparency)
- progress-box.png    - Progress bar background (recommended: 400x20 PNG)
- progress-bar.png    - Progress bar fill (recommended: 400x20 PNG, purple gradient)

Color Scheme:
- Background Top:    #6366f1 (Indigo)
- Background Bottom: #8b5cf6 (Purple)
- Text:              #ffffff (White)

Installation:
1. Copy this directory to /usr/share/plymouth/themes/winux/
2. Install the theme:
   sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/share/plymouth/themes/default.plymouth default.plymouth /usr/share/plymouth/themes/winux/winux.plymouth 100
3. Set as default:
   sudo update-alternatives --set default.plymouth /usr/share/plymouth/themes/winux/winux.plymouth
4. Update initramfs:
   sudo update-initramfs -u

Testing:
- Preview: sudo plymouthd; sudo plymouth --show-splash; sleep 5; sudo plymouth quit
